    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dings, while the interior shows consistent wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or a suspension tune-up. It's a solid, honest car that offers great value for a buyer willing to overlook some cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
